data.description:
Professional photographs coming soon.
Welcome to your new home in Norwood Young America! This 4-bed, 2-bath split-level gem boasts a meticulously maintained interior, freshly painted exterior, and the added comfort of a new water heater and newer furnace. Ideal for families seeking both style and functionality. Make your move and experience the charm of this well-kept property. Further, Enjoy outdoor living on the large deck in the backyard, perfect for gatherings and relaxation. The large insulated garage provides ample storage space, making it an ideal haven for your vehicles and more.
